 - Southbound Wong Nai Chung Road between Sports Road and Shan Kwong Road ; and



 - Northbound Wong Nai Chung Road between Shan Kwong Road and Hau Tak Lane.




 Vehicles may not be permitted to access or leave car parks along the route during the road closure period.




