 At around 10pm, a large number of violent protestors vandalised facilities at Taikoo MTR Station, including escalators and CCTV. They also illegally occupied King's Road.  Having given repeated warnings but in vain, Police officers have deployed tear gas and appropriate force to disperse the violent protestors.




