 Wong Cheuk-man, aged 81, went missing after he left his residence in Wang Tau Hom Estate yesterday morning (September 12). His family made a report to Police on the same day.




 He is about 1.65 metres tall, 50 kilograms in weight and of thin build. He has a long face with yellow complexion and short greyish-white hair. He was last seen wearing a white vest, blue jeans and blue slippers.




